Feb 23(Reuters) - Beijing Tensyn Digital Marketing Technology Joint Stock Co
* Says it and its top shareholder signed a strategic cooperation framework agreement with a Qingdao-based asset management firm, mainly regarding development of cultural industry of Laoshan District
